title: Fabulous 794 sq ft 2 bed, 1 bath in sought-after Covington area
posting_body: ['Covington Place Senior', 'Visit Our Community Today!', '26902 169th Place Southeast', 'Covington, WA 98042', 'show contact info', 'Welcome to Covington Place Senior', 'Covington Place offers something for everyone.', 'Our residents enjoy everything from our community room and rooftop patio to our computer lab and library.', 'Some of our homes include private decks and patios, walk-in closets, and kitchen pantries.', 'Experience quality affordable senior living in Covington.', "You'll love our one and two-bedroom apartment homes.", 'Our residents enjoy a variety of amenities to enhance their lifestyles.', 'Our two-bedroom Meridian floor plan features walk-in closets, dine-in kitchen, and a pantry.', 'Bedrooms: 2 |  Bathrooms:  1', 'Square Footage:', '794 sq ft', 'Rental Pricing: $1747/Month', 'Our Residents Enjoy:', '● activities room', '● Computer Lab', '● Library', '● Media Room', '● On-Site Management', '● Patio', '● Planned Social Activities', '● Social Room', '● 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', '● Close to Shopping & Dining', '● Community Rooms', '● On-Site Salon', '● Rooftop Patio', 'This Unit Comes With:', '● Deck/Patio Available', '● Dining Area', '● Dishwasher', '● Fully-Equipped Kitchen', '● Range', '● Refrigerator', '● Walk-In Closet Available in select unit', '● 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', '● Close to Shopping & Dining', '● Community Rooms', '● On-Site Salon', '● Rooftop Patio', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'Phone-Number:', 'show contact info', 'Pet-Policy:', 'Lease-Length: 6-Month', 'From WA-18 E: Turn right onto SE 272nd', 'St and turn left onto 168th Ple SE.', 'Turn left onto SE 168th Pl and Covington Place will be on your left.', 'Please call us for driving directions.', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '1BE9EFAD50324AA']
